chatSession.message: Hey there! How are you doing?
Hi! I'm good, thanks. How about you?
I'm doing well, just working on a project.
Sounds interesting! What project are you working on?
I'm building a chat screen for a Flutter app.
Nice! Do you need any help with that?
Yes, I'm trying to figure out the best way to handle real-time messages.
You can use WebSockets for real-time communication. Have you looked into that?
I have, but I'm not sure how to integrate it with my state management solution.
I can help with that. Let's look at your code together.
